// Test 3: Tous les 7 mots-cles et toutes les 5 unites de vitesse
// Mots-cles: CAST SURGE INVERT LOCK BOOST NULLIFY PHASE
// Unites: kms mps warp swift crawl
CAST meteor_charge 999kms ##
SURGE lightning_veil 3.14mps ##
INVERT void_drift 1warp ##
LOCK frost_anchor 0.5swift ##
BOOST feather_run 1crawl ##
NULLIFY time_wall 100kms ##
PHASE echo_step 7.77mps ##
